Sentencas: Scattered and linked microcracks in the electrolyte layer have been analysed in detail in anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Scattered and linked microcracks in solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte

Sentencas: The empirical model established allowed critical characteristics of scattered and localised microcracking to be determined using electrolyte microstructural parameters.
Titulo: Scattered and linked microcracks in solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte

Sentencas: The model was verified with experimental data obtained for electron beam deposited scandia-stabilised zirconia electrolytes.
Titulo: Scattered and linked microcracks in solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte

Sentencas: Suitable annealing and deposition temperatures during fuel cell fabrication could be predicted from the critical temperature difference below which microcracking does not occur.
Titulo: Scattered and linked microcracks in solid oxide fuel cell electrolyte
